thread.title_full: Mexico cenbank sells $141 mln at 16.8509 pesos at daily auction | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Mexico cenbank sells $141 mln at 16.8509 pesos at daily auction
text:
MEXICO CITY Aug 27 The central bank of Mexico sold $141 million on Thursday of $200 million offered at an average price of 16.8509 pesos per dollar, the bank said.
The auction is part of an program to boost foreign exchange liquidity following a slump in the peso currency, which firmed strongly on Thursday.
